Amendment No. 1 to House Bill 1877
Amend House Bill 1877 as engrossed H4/7/25 (version: 4/7/25 10:44:55 AM):
Page 1, delete line 33, and substitute the following:
"in whole or in part, through the use of artificial intelligence;"
